{
  "video_id": "_pQ1BCdSTTI",
  "title": "Smelfies, and other experiments in synthetic biology | Ani Liu",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 14555.0,
      "text": "What if our plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14580.0,
      "end_time": 17276.0,
      "text": "could sense the toxicity levels in the soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17300.0,
      "end_time": 20340.0,
      "text": "and express that toxicity through the color of its leaves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21500.0,
      "end_time": 24820.0,
      "text": "What if those plants could also remove those toxins from the soil?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26380.0,
      "end_time": 28476.0,
      "text": "Instead, what if those plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28500.0,
      "end_time": 30356.0,
      "text": "grew their own packaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30380.0,
      "end_time": 32955.0,
      "text": "or were designed to only be harvested"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32980.0,
      "end_time": 35236.0,
      "text": "by their owners&#39; own patented machines?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37156.0,
      "text": "What happens when biological design"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37180.0,
      "end_time": 40716.0,
      "text": "is driven by the motivations of mass-produced commodities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40740.0,
      "end_time": 42340.0,
      "text": "What kind of world would that be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43600.0,
      "end_time": 47760.0,
      "text": "My name is Ani, and I&#39;m a designer and researcher at MIT Media Lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47100.0,
      "end_time": 51236.0,
      "text": "where I&#39;m part of a relatively new and unique group called Design Fiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 55355.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;re wedged somewhere between science fiction and science fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55380.0,
      "end_time": 59516.0,
      "text": "And at MIT, I am lucky enough to rub shoulders with scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59540.0,
      "end_time": 61516.0,
      "text": "studying all kinds of cutting edge fields"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61540.0,
      "end_time": 63916.0,
      "text": "like synthetic neurobiology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63940.0,
      "end_time": 65956.0,
      "text": "artificial intelligence, artificial life"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65980.0,
      "end_time": 67716.0,
      "text": "and everything in between."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67740.0,
      "end_time": 71556.0,
      "text": "And across campus, there&#39;s truly brilliant scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71580.0,
      "end_time": 75760.0,
      "text": "asking questions like, \"How can I make the world a better place?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75100.0,
      "end_time": 77996.0,
      "text": "And part of what my group likes to ask is, \"What is better?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78200.0,
      "end_time": 80116.0,
      "text": "What is better for you, for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80140.0,
      "end_time": 82276.0,
      "text": "for a white woman, a gay man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82300.0,
      "end_time": 84795.0,
      "text": "a veteran, a child with a prosthetic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84820.0,
      "end_time": 86875.0,
      "text": "Technology is never neutral."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86900.0,
      "end_time": 88556.0,
      "text": "It frames a reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88580.0,
      "end_time": 90356.0,
      "text": "and reflects a context."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90380.0,
      "end_time": 94116.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine what it would say about the work-life balance at your office"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94140.0,
      "end_time": 96316.0,
      "text": "if these were standard issue on the first day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96340.0,
      "end_time": 97756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97780.0,
      "end_time": 100360.0,
      "text": "I believe it&#39;s the role of artists and designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100600.0,
      "end_time": 102196.0,
      "text": "to raise critical questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102220.0,
      "end_time": 104636.0,
      "text": "Art is how you can see and feel the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104660.0,
      "end_time": 107116.0,
      "text": "and today is an exciting time to be a designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107140.0,
      "end_time": 109276.0,
      "text": "for all the new tools becoming accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109300.0,
      "end_time": 110875.0,
      "text": "For instance, synthetic biology"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110900.0,
      "end_time": 113796.0,
      "text": "seeks to write biology as a design problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113820.0,
      "end_time": 115356.0,
      "text": "And through these developments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115380.0,
      "end_time": 118316.0,
      "text": "my lab asks, what are the roles and responsibilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118340.0,
      "end_time": 122676.0,
      "text": "of an artist, designer, scientist or businessman?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122700.0,
      "end_time": 124236.0,
      "text": "What are the implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126996.0,
      "text": "of synthetic biology, genetic engineering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127200.0,
      "end_time": 131636.0,
      "text": "and how are they shaping our notions of what it means to be a human?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131660.0,
      "end_time": 134956.0,
      "text": "What are the implications of this on society, on evolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134980.0,
      "end_time": 137555.0,
      "text": "and what are the stakes in this game?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137580.0,
      "end_time": 140796.0,
      "text": "My own speculative design research at the current moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140820.0,
      "end_time": 142236.0,
      "text": "plays with synthetic biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145275.0,
      "text": "but for more emotionally driven output."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145300.0,
      "end_time": 148760.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m obsessed with olfaction as a design space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148100.0,
      "end_time": 150916.0,
      "text": "and this project started with this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150940.0,
      "end_time": 154716.0,
      "text": "of what if you could take a smell selfie, a smelfie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154740.0,
      "end_time": 156196.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156220.0,
      "end_time": 158956.0,
      "text": "What if you could take your own natural body odor"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158980.0,
      "end_time": 161360.0,
      "text": "and send it to a lover?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161600.0,
      "end_time": 164836.0,
      "text": "Funny enough, I found that this was a 19th century Austrian tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164860.0,
      "end_time": 167476.0,
      "text": "where couples in courtship would keep a slice of apple"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167500.0,
      "end_time": 170760.0,
      "text": "crammed under their armpit during dances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170100.0,
      "end_time": 171636.0,
      "text": "and at the end of the evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171660.0,
      "end_time": 175360.0,
      "text": "the girl would give the guy she most fancied her used fruit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175600.0,
      "end_time": 177236.0,
      "text": "and if the feeling was mutual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 179196.0,
      "text": "he would wolf down that stinky apple."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 179220.0,
      "end_time": 182340.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 183500.0,
      "end_time": 186796.0,
      "text": "Famously, Napoleon wrote many love letters to Josephine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186820.0,
      "end_time": 191760.0,
      "text": "but perhaps amongst the most memorable is this brief and urgent note:"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191100.0,
      "end_time": 193316.0,
      "text": "\"Home in three days. Don&#39;t bathe.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193340.0,
      "end_time": 195396.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195420.0,
      "end_time": 197579.0,
      "text": "Both Napoleon and Josephine adored violets."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199140.0,
      "end_time": 201275.0,
      "text": "Josephine wore violet-scented perfume,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201300.0,
      "end_time": 203116.0,
      "text": "carried violets on their wedding day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203140.0,
      "end_time": 205154.0,
      "text": "and Napoleon sent her a bouquet of violets"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205179.0,
      "end_time": 206716.0,
      "text": "every year on their anniversary."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 206740.0,
      "end_time": 208316.0,
      "text": "When Josephine passed away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208340.0,
      "end_time": 209916.0,
      "text": "he planted violets at her grave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 209940.0,
      "end_time": 211756.0,
      "text": "and just before his exile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 211780.0,
      "end_time": 213916.0,
      "text": "he went back to that tomb site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 213940.0,
      "end_time": 216596.0,
      "text": "picked some of those flowers, entombed them in a locket"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 216620.0,
      "end_time": 218356.0,
      "text": "and wore them until the day he died."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 218380.0,
      "end_time": 219916.0,
      "text": "And I found this so moving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219940.0,
      "end_time": 223835.0,
      "text": "I thought, could I engineer that violet to smell just like Josephine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 223860.0,
      "end_time": 225516.0,
      "text": "What if, for the rest of eternity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 225540.0,
      "end_time": 227116.0,
      "text": "when you went to visit her site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 227140.0,
      "end_time": 230396.0,
      "text": "you could smell Josephine just as Napoleon loved her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 230420.0,
      "end_time": 232835.0,
      "text": "Could we engineer new ways of mourning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 232860.0,
      "end_time": 234956.0,
      "text": "new rituals for remembering?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 234980.0,
      "end_time": 237676.0,
      "text": "After all, we&#39;ve engineered transgenic crops"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 237700.0,
      "end_time": 239835.0,
      "text": "to be maximized for profit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 239860.0,
      "end_time": 241996.0,
      "text": "crops that stand up to transport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 242200.0,
      "end_time": 243956.0,
      "text": "crops that have a long shelf life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 243980.0,
      "end_time": 246435.0,
      "text": "crops that taste sugary sweet but resist pests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 246460.0,
      "end_time": 249876.0,
      "text": "sometimes at the expense of nutritional value."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 249900.0,
      "end_time": 254476.0,
      "text": "Can we harness these same technologies for an emotionally sensitive output?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 254500.0,
      "end_time": 255796.0,
      "text": "So currently in my lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255820.0,
      "end_time": 259116.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m researching questions like, what makes a human smell like a human?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 259140.0,
      "end_time": 261755.0,
      "text": "And it turns out it&#39;s fairly complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 261779.0,
      "end_time": 264996.0,
      "text": "Factors such as your diet, your medications, your lifestyle"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 265200.0,
      "end_time": 267360.0,
      "text": "all factor into the way you smell."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 267600.0,
      "end_time": 269596.0,
      "text": "And I found that our sweat is mostly odorless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269620.0,
      "end_time": 271755.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s our bacteria and microbiome"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271779.0,
      "end_time": 275516.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s responsible for your smells, your mood, your identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 275540.0,
      "end_time": 277156.0,
      "text": "and so much beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277180.0,
      "end_time": 279476.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s all kinds of molecules that you emit"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279500.0,
      "end_time": 281780.0,
      "text": "but which we only perceive subconsciously."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 282940.0,
      "end_time": 285276.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve been cataloging and collecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 285300.0,
      "end_time": 287476.0,
      "text": "bacteria from different sites of my body."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 287500.0,
      "end_time": 289476.0,
      "text": "After talking to a scientist, we thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 289500.0,
      "end_time": 291196.0,
      "text": "maybe the perfect concoction of Ani"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 291220.0,
      "end_time": 295196.0,
      "text": "is like 10 percent collarbone, 30 percent underarm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 295220.0,
      "end_time": 297516.0,
      "text": "40 percent bikini line and so forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 297540.0,
      "end_time": 300596.0,
      "text": "and occasionally I let researchers from other labs"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 300620.0,
      "end_time": 302276.0,
      "text": "take a sniff of my samples."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 302300.0,
      "end_time": 305476.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s been interesting to hear how smell of the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 305500.0,
      "end_time": 308316.0,
      "text": "is perceived outside of the context of the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 308340.0,
      "end_time": 309916.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve gotten feedback such as,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 309940.0,
      "end_time": 312396.0,
      "text": "smells like flowers, like chicken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 312420.0,
      "end_time": 313636.0,
      "text": "like cornflakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313660.0,
      "end_time": 315116.0,
      "text": "like beef carnitas."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315140.0,
      "end_time": 317360.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317600.0,
      "end_time": 320676.0,
      "text": "At the same time, I cultivate a set of carnivorous plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 320700.0,
      "end_time": 324356.0,
      "text": "for their ability to emit fleshlike odors to attract prey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324380.0,
      "end_time": 327195.0,
      "text": "in an attempt to kind of create this symbiotic relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 327220.0,
      "end_time": 330140.0,
      "text": "between my bacteria and this organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 331340.0,
      "end_time": 333996.0,
      "text": "And as it so happens, I&#39;m at MIT and I&#39;m in a bar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 334200.0,
      "end_time": 336316.0,
      "text": "and I was talking to a scientist"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 336340.0,
      "end_time": 338715.0,
      "text": "who happens to be a chemist and a plant scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 338740.0,
      "end_time": 340636.0,
      "text": "and I was telling him about my project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 340660.0,
      "end_time": 343796.0,
      "text": "and he was like, \"Well, this sounds like botany for lonely women.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 343820.0,
      "end_time": 346836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 346860.0,
      "end_time": 349756.0,
      "text": "Unperturbed, I said, \"OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 349780.0,
      "end_time": 350996.0,
      "text": "I challenged him."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 351200.0,
      "end_time": 354316.0,
      "text": "\"Can we engineer a plant that can love me back?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 354340.0,
      "end_time": 357796.0,
      "text": "And for some reason, he was like, \"Sure, why not?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 357820.0,
      "end_time": 360756.0,
      "text": "So we started with, can we get a plant to grow towards me"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 360780.0,
      "end_time": 362236.0,
      "text": "like I was the sun?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 366195.0,
      "text": "And so we&#39;re looking at mechanisms in plants such as phototropism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 366220.0,
      "end_time": 368396.0,
      "text": "which causes the plant to grow towards the sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 368420.0,
      "end_time": 370396.0,
      "text": "by producing hormones like auxin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 370420.0,
      "end_time": 373760.0,
      "text": "which causes cell elongation on the shady side."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 373100.0,
      "end_time": 375236.0,
      "text": "And right now I&#39;m creating a set of lipsticks"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377750.0,
      "text": "that are infused with these chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 377100.0,
      "end_time": 380756.0,
      "text": "that allow me to interact with a plant on its own chemical signatures --"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 380780.0,
      "end_time": 384195.0,
      "text": "lipsticks that cause plants to grow where I kiss it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 384220.0,
      "end_time": 386956.0,
      "text": "plants that blossom where I kiss the bloom."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 386980.0,
      "end_time": 389756.0,
      "text": "And through these projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 389780.0,
      "end_time": 391195.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m asking questions like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 391220.0,
      "end_time": 392916.0,
      "text": "how do we define nature?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 392940.0,
      "end_time": 396476.0,
      "text": "How do we define nature when we can reengineer its properties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 396500.0,
      "end_time": 397916.0,
      "text": "and when should we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 397940.0,
      "end_time": 401636.0,
      "text": "Should we do it for profit, for utility?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 401660.0,
      "end_time": 403356.0,
      "text": "Can we do it for emotional ends?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 403380.0,
      "end_time": 406956.0,
      "text": "Can biotechnology be used to create work as moving as music?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 406980.0,
      "end_time": 408876.0,
      "text": "What are the thresholds between science"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 408900.0,
      "end_time": 411739.0,
      "text": "and its ability to shape our emotional landscape?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 412460.0,
      "end_time": 416236.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a famous design mantra that form follows function."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 420316.0,
      "text": "Well, now, wedged somewhere between science, design and art"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 420340.0,
      "end_time": 421556.0,
      "text": "I get to ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 421580.0,
      "end_time": 423360.0,
      "text": "what if fiction informs fact?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 423600.0,
      "end_time": 425116.0,
      "text": "What kind of R&D lab would that look like"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 425140.0,
      "end_time": 427756.0,
      "text": "and what kind of questions would we ask together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 427780.0,
      "end_time": 430116.0,
      "text": "We often look to technology as the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 430140.0,
      "end_time": 431676.0,
      "text": "but as an artist and designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 431700.0,
      "end_time": 434195.0,
      "text": "I like to ask, but what is the question?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 434220.0,
      "end_time": 435436.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 435460.0,
      "end_time": 438820.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}